trans:
Missions :
- Provide guests with a warm and efficient welcome in line with the hotel's quality standards;
- Performs IT and administrative procedures related to check-in/check-out on the computer system in place in the hotel
- Verify guests guarantees and bookings;
- Ensures the follow-up of guests' stays by communicating important information to colleagues and superiors, and by checking guarantees;
- Answers phone calls and takes bookings on time;
- Maintains, checks and controls personal cash box;
- Responds to various guest requests and follows up to ensure guest satisfaction;
- Provides guests with tourist information;
- Carries out various projects assigned by line management;
- Implements procedures and policies defined by the brand and the hotel in terms of guest control and personal safety;
- Ensures that special guest requests are forwarded to the appropriate departments;
- Knows the hotel's services, informs guests of their requests and prompts them to use them, and suggests that guests make a booking;
